175 A.3d 174 MONTCLAIR STATE UNIVERSITY, PLAINTIFF-RESPONDENT, v. COUNTY OF PASSAIC, DEFENDANT, AND CITY OF CLIFTON, DEFENDANT-PETITIONER.

C-328 September Term 2017

080084 November 29, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-003318-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is granted.
